-- Astaldi Gets $80 Million Construction Contract at Refinery in Saudi Arabia
-- Tommaso Ebhardt
-- 2010-06-16T08:21:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/astaldi-gets-80-million-construction-contract-at-refinery-in-saudi-arabia.html

          
          
             Astaldi SpA got an $80 million
contract to carry out “civil works” for the construction of an
oil refinery at Jubail, Saudi Arabia, according to a statement
distributed by the Italian exchange.  
          
          


  


        